        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for specimen of <hi rend="italic">Drosophyllum</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Describes capacity of various plants to catch flies.</p>
            <p>Cannot name fern specimen.</p> 
<p>Laugher pigeon descended from <hi rend="italic">Columba livia</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Discusses tailless dogs.</p>
            <p>Believes astronomical phenomenon responsible for oscillation of level of earth’s crust.</p> 
<p>Would WCT like copy of <hi rend="italic">Orchids</hi>?</p>  
<p>Expected plants [<hi rend="italic">Drosophyllum</hi>] have arrived.</p> 
        </abstract>
